Class EspDialog

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.nenick.espressomacchiato.elements.EspView
      • de.nenick.espressomacchiato.elements.EspDialog
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    EspAlertDialog, EspSupportAlertDialog

    public class EspDialog
extends EspView

    Base for action and assertion for Dialogs.

    Recommend is to use more specific subclasses like EspAlertDialog.
